<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 10:04:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列集结军队发动袭击，巴勒斯坦人逃离加沙北部</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-flee-northern-gaza-as-israel-masses-troops-for-assault/articleshow/104421804.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104421804.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着以色列继续空袭并准备地面攻击，数千名巴勒斯坦人正在逃离加沙地带北部。以色列要求居民在周六早上之前向南迁移，并承诺保持两条道路畅通，供他们逃生。然而，由于拥挤和缺乏安全走廊，许多巴勒斯坦人无法离开。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 09:47:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-flee-northern-gaza-as-israel-masses-troops-for-assault/articleshow/104421804.cms</guid></item><item><title>更多援助航班抵达埃及西奈半岛，等待飞往加沙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/more-aid-flights-arrive-in-egypts-sinai-awaiting-passage-to-gaza/articleshow/104421811.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104421811.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新的援助航班已抵达埃及西奈半岛，救援物资将被存放在那里，直到确保安全进入加沙地带。连接西奈半岛和加沙地带的拉法过境点在埃及一侧仍然开放，尽管交通因以色列的轰炸而中断。埃及安全部队加强了边境一侧的安全，但有关封锁过境点的报道是不正确的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 09:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/more-aid-flights-arrive-in-egypts-sinai-awaiting-passage-to-gaza/articleshow/104421811.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗外长从贝鲁特警告以色列可能遭受“大地震”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-minister-warns-israel-from-beirut-it-could-suffer-a-huge-earthquake/articleshow/104421487.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104421487.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗外长呼吁以色列停止对加沙的袭击，并警告说，如果真主党加入战斗，战争可能会扩大到中东其他地区。他表示，真主党已经考虑了所有可能发生战争的情况，以色列应立即停止对加沙的袭击。以色列将真主党视为最严重的威胁，拥有数千枚火箭和导弹。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 09:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-foreign-minister-warns-israel-from-beirut-it-could-suffer-a-huge-earthquake/articleshow/104421487.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚人拒绝原住民权利公投：政府</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australians-reject-indigenous-rights-referendum-govt/articleshow/104421430.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104421430.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 09:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australians-reject-indigenous-rights-referendum-govt/articleshow/104421430.cms</guid></item><item><title>新西兰国家党已准备好组建新政府</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealands-national-party-well-positioned-to-form-new-government/articleshow/104420980.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104420980.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由 Christopher Luxon 领导的新西兰中右翼国家党准备与其首选的联盟党 ACT 组建新政府，因为早期结果表明他们可能在大选中获得多数席位。国家党获得41%的选票，而执政党工党则获得26%的选票。选举委员会预计，国家党和首都领地联合起来将拥有足够的席位来组建政府，而无需第三方。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 09:15:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/new-zealands-national-party-well-positioned-to-form-new-government/articleshow/104420980.cms</guid></item><item><title>沙特暂停与以色列关系正常化谈判：消息人士</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-pauses-talks-on-normalisation-with-israel-source/articleshow/104420595.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104420595.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，由于以色列和哈马斯之间持续的冲突，沙特阿拉伯暂停了与以色列关系正常化的谈判。这个从未承认以色列的海湾王国一直在考虑在某些条件下实现正常化。美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将与沙特外长会面。沙特阿拉伯越来越关注加沙地带的局势，并一直在与地区领导人接触，以解决不断升级的暴力事件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 08:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-pauses-talks-on-normalisation-with-israel-source/articleshow/104420595.cms</guid></item><item><title>教师遇害后法国将部署7000名士兵</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-to-deploy-7000-soldiers-after-teachers-slaying/articleshow/104417543.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104417543.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在阿拉斯一所学校发生致命刺伤事件后，法国将部署 7000 名士兵。这次袭击由一名车臣籍男子实施，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将其称为“伊斯兰恐怖”行为。随着法国将警戒级别提升至最高级别，这些士兵将于周一晚上部署。马克龙还提到，安全部队挫败了另一次未遂袭击。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 06:42:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/france-to-deploy-7000-soldiers-after-teachers-slaying/articleshow/104417543.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗北部什叶派清真寺发生爆炸 17人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blast-rips-through-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan-many-casualties-feared/articleshow/104402762.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104402762.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据医院官员和目击者称，周五祈祷期间，阿富汗北部一座什叶派清真寺发生爆炸，造成至少 17 人死亡，另有 15 人重伤。然而塔利班官员声称，爆炸中只有七人死亡。目前还没有任何恐怖组织立即声称对此次袭击负责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 12:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/blast-rips-through-shiite-mosque-in-northern-afghanistan-many-casualties-feared/articleshow/104402762.cms</guid></item><item><title>世卫组织呼吁立即撤销加沙撤离令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-pleads-for-immediate-reversal-of-gaza-evacuation-order-to-protect-health-reduce-suffering/articleshow/104412410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104412410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;世界卫生组织（WHO）呼吁在加沙紧急建立人道主义走廊，以确保安全运送援助物资。持续的空袭和关闭边界使平民无处可去。以色列军方已指示加沙北部 110 万人撤离，世界卫生组织称这对患者、卫生工作者和平民来说是灾难性的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 02:45:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-pleads-for-immediate-reversal-of-gaza-evacuation-order-to-protect-health-reduce-suffering/articleshow/104412410.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列称军队在加沙进行小规模袭击以挫败哈马斯组织</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-troops-carried-out-small-raids-in-gaza-to-thwart-hamas-cells/articleshow/104411859.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411859.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列宣布在加沙地带与哈马斯的冲突中已从空战转向地面行动。以色列军队在坦克的支援下，对巴勒斯坦火箭人员进行了小规模袭击，并收集了人质位置的信息。内塔尼亚胡总理誓言要摧毁哈马斯，而一些国家则敦促以色列暂缓进攻。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 02:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-says-troops-carried-out-small-raids-in-gaza-to-thwart-hamas-cells/articleshow/104411859.cms</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，沙特阿拉伯在战争中搁置与以色列的协议，并与伊朗接触</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-puts-israel-deal-on-ice-amid-war-engages-with-iran-sources-say/articleshow/104411723.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411723.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，随着以色列和哈马斯之间的冲突升级，沙特阿拉伯暂停了与以色列关系正常化的计划。沙特王国还与伊朗进行了接触，沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼接到了伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西的电话。与以色列关系正常化谈判的推迟表明，以色列对巴勒斯坦人的让步问题将成为未来更重要的优先事项</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:51:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-puts-israel-deal-on-ice-amid-war-engages-with-iran-sources-say/articleshow/104411723.cms</guid></item><item><title>“死亡比离开更好”：尽管以色列声称哈马斯将加沙平民用作人盾，但加沙平民拒绝撤离“地狱”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-is-better-than-leaving-gaza-civilians-refuse-to-evacuate-hellhole-despite-israel-claiming-hamas-are-using-them-as-human-shields/articleshow/104411547.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411547.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管接到了 24 小时撤离通知，但加沙的许多人还是选择留下来面对潜在的死亡，而不是放弃家园。联合国宣布加沙局势难以为继，电力供应被切断，重要资源变得稀缺。哈马斯鼓励人们留在原地，而以色列则认为他们必须消灭这个恐怖组织。联合国对平民流离失所表示关切。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/death-is-better-than-leaving-gaza-civilians-refuse-to-evacuate-hellhole-despite-israel-claiming-hamas-are-using-them-as-human-shields/articleshow/104411547.cms</guid></item><item><title>所有注册政党都有资格参加民意调查：巴基斯坦总理</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/all-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar/articleshow/104419055.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104419055.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦临时总理安瓦鲁尔·哈克·卡卡尔表示，所有在巴基斯坦选举委员会注册的政党都将被允许参加即将举行的选举。由于伊姆兰·汗入狱，人们对伊姆兰·汗所在政党 PTI 的命运感到担忧。卡卡尔还排除了与被禁止的巴基斯坦塔利班运动进行谈判的可能性，并表示非法居住在巴基斯坦的阿富汗国民将被遣返。他表达了与喀布尔建立健康关系的愿望，但强调只有一小部分阿富汗国民参与了不良活动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 07:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/all-registered-political-parties-eligible-to-take-part-in-polls-pakistan-pm-anwaarul-haq-kakar/articleshow/104419055.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备入侵加沙，美国看不到下一步计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hamas-israel-war-as-israel-readies-gaza-invasion-us-sees-no-plan-for-whats-next/articleshow/104411430.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411430.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登政府担心以色列没有针对加沙地带潜在地面入侵的后果的计划。白宫正在敦促以色列超越消灭哈马斯的眼前目标，并考虑长期冲突的后果。美国还担心加沙的人道主义伤亡以及该地区人质和美国公民的命运。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:34:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hamas-israel-war-as-israel-readies-gaza-invasion-us-sees-no-plan-for-whats-next/articleshow/104411430.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗敦促美国“控制”以色列以避免地区战争</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/world/middle-east/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/articleshow/104411472.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411571.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗最高外交官周五在贝鲁特表示，美国必须控制以色列，以避免与哈马斯的战争在地区蔓延，并补充说德黑兰正在寻求维护黎巴嫩的安全。外交部长侯赛因·阿米尔-阿卜杜拉希安表示：“如果美国人想要阻止该地区的战争发展，他们就必须控制以色列。”他补充道，“我们此行的目标之一就是强调黎巴嫩的安全”</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/world/middle-east/iran-urges-us-to-control-israel-to-avert-regional-war/articleshow/104411472.cms</guid></item><item><title>真主党表示“准备好”在时机成熟时对以色列采取行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-prepared-for-action-against-israel-when-time-comes/articleshow/104411418.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411418.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗支持的黎巴嫩真主党运动周五表示，将“做好充分准备”，在时机成熟时加入其盟友哈马斯对以色列的战争。他说：“我们已经做好充分准备，当需要采取行动时，我们会采取行动。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:14:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hezbollah-says-prepared-for-action-against-israel-when-time-comes/articleshow/104411418.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国一学校发生刺伤事件 一名教师死亡 两人受伤 疑似恐怖袭击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-teacher-dies-and-2-people-are-wounded-in-a-stabbing-in-a-french-school-terrorism-is-suspected/articleshow/104411047.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411047.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国反恐检察官宣布，他们正在接手对法国北部一所学校周五发生的持刀袭击事件的调查，该袭击事件导致一名教师死亡，另外两人受伤。国家反恐检察厅启动调查，指出此次袭击涉嫌恐怖动机</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/a-teacher-dies-and-2-people-are-wounded-in-a-stabbing-in-a-french-school-terrorism-is-suspected/articleshow/104411047.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称，以色列对加沙逃亡车队的袭击造成 70 人死亡，其中大部分是妇女和儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-70-people-mostly-women-and-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gazas-fleeing-convoys/articleshow/104411652.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104411652.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯官员报告称，以色列对离开加沙城的车队进行空袭，导致约 70 人死亡，其中主要是妇女和儿童。空袭针对的是从加沙城向南行驶的三个不同地点的车辆。</description><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 01:44:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/hamas-says-70-people-mostly-women-and-children-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gazas-fleeing-convoys/articleshow/104411652.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃及反对派候选人结束总统选举竞选活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/egyptian-opposition-candidate-ends-campaign-for-presidential-poll/articleshow/104410967.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410967.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在即将举行的选举中埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西的潜在挑战者艾哈迈德·坦塔维宣布，由于未获得所需数量的公众支持，他将不会参加竞选。坦塔维的竞选团队声称，官员和亲政府暴徒阻碍了他们争取支持的努力，而安全部队则逮捕了他的支持者并阻止了竞选活动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:36:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/egyptian-opposition-candidate-ends-campaign-for-presidential-poll/articleshow/104410967.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯当局在突袭后拘留了被监禁的反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的三名律师</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-authorities-detain-3-lawyers-for-imprisoned-opposition-leader-alexei-navalny-after-raids/articleshow/104410950.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/104410950.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的三名律师在其住宅被搜查后被俄罗斯当局拘留。此举被视为试图进一步孤立纳瓦尔尼。这些律师因被指控参与极端主义团体而成为刑事案件的一部分。纳瓦尔尼自 2021 年 1 月以来一直被监禁，并面临多项指控，他声称这些指控是出于政治动机。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 23:30:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-authorities-detain-3-lawyers-for-imprisoned-opposition-leader-alexei-navalny-after-raids/articleshow/104410950.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>